title: Teams you can "stick a fork in" & Team of ATL
itunes:title: Teams you can "stick a fork in" & Team of ATL
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling, and Marc Sessler – make their final pick for the 2015 Team of ATL. Then the heroes break down which teams you can "stick a fork in" after Week 3. Plus, a recap of the Monday night football game between the Kansas City Chiefs and the Green Bay Packers.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
